sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Disp as OutboxDispatcher<br/>(BackgroundService — ADR-025)
    participant Outbox as IOutboxRepository
    participant Pub as IEventPublisher<br/>[MassTransit IPublishEndpoint]
    participant MQ as RabbitMQ<br/>(exchange: TransactionRegistered)

    loop a cada 1s (IdleDelay) ou logo em seguida se houve trabalho
        Note over Disp: AsyncScope novo a cada iteração<br/>(DapperUnitOfWork é IAsyncDisposable)

        Disp->>Outbox: PeekPendingAsync(batchSize=50)
        Outbox-->>Disp: List<OutboxEntry> ordenado por seq ASC

        alt lista vazia
            Note over Disp: Task.Delay(1s) e tenta de novo
        else há eventos pendentes
            loop for each entry (FIFO)
                Disp->>Pub: PublishAsync(TransactionRegistered)
                Pub->>MQ: AMQP publish

                alt publish OK
                    Disp->>Outbox: MarkPublishedAsync(entry.Id)<br/>(SET published_at = NOW())
                else publish falha
                    Disp->>Outbox: RecordFailureAsync(entry.Id, error)<br/>(attempts++, last_error)
                    Note over Disp: break do loop —<br/>preserva FIFO, não pula evento
                end
            end
        end
    end

    Note over Disp,MQ: Falha transiente (NpgsqlException/SocketException/TimeoutException):<br/>log uma WRN no início do outage + suprime stack até recuperar
